    "biography": "<p><b>Appearance:</b> A ragged, vaguely manshaped shard of darkness. As it looms closer, the demonically twisted face of the bishop can be discerned, complete with mitre. The shade of Bishop Hatto is wholly insubstantial and cannot be engaged in combat, nor does he have meaningful Characteristics -- he owes his existence to his overwhelming hate.</p>",
